" style="animation-duration: 0s;"><div class="sc" style="width: 1200px;"><div data-sid="testimonial_melanie_0" class="sie-testimonial_melanie_0 se" style="transform: scale(1, 1) translate(0px, 0px);"><p class="se-t sie-testimonial_melanie_0-text st-m-heading st-d-heading se-rc">- Melanie&nbsp;</p></div><div data-sid="testimonial_melanie_1" class="sie-testimonial_melanie_1 se" style="transform: scale(1, 1) translate(0px, 0px);"><p class="se-t sie-testimonial_melanie_1-text st-m-title st-d-title se-rc">From the moment I discovered Nandon Klinton’s work, I knew she had to be part of my wedding day. We were married in Bali in August 2019, and she captured every moment so effortlessly - half the time I didn’t even realise she was there, yet she still caught all the magic, emotion and tiny details.<br><br>Since then, Nandon Klinton has photographed our growing family every single year, and it’s become a tradition. As a mum, I’m always the one behind the camera, so having these beautiful, magical photos of me with my children is something I’ll hold onto forever.<br></p></div></div></div><div id="testimonial_yiota" class="ss sis-testimonial_yiota sactive" style="animation-duration: 0s;"><div class="sc" style="width: 1200px;"><div data-sid="testimonial_yiota_0" class="sie-testimonial_yiota_0 se" style="transform: scale(1, 1) translate(0px, 0px);"><p class="se-t sie-testimonial_yiota_0-text st-m-heading st-d-heading se-rc">- Yiota</p></div><div data-sid="testimonial_yiota_1" class="sie-testimonial_yiota_1 se" style="transform: scale(1, 1) translate(0px, 0px);"><p class="se-t sie-testimonial_yiota_1-text st-m-title st-d-title se-rc">I’ve worked with many photographers and Nandon Klinton was by far one of the best experiences I’ve had. Her genuine, kind demeanour made me and my husband feel extremely comfortable throughout the entire photo shoot. Not only was the photo shoot a breeze but the photos that we ended up with were beyond better than I was imagining! Thank you so much for my beautiful memories that I will treasure forever. You are truly amazing</p></div></div></div><div id="testimonial_tai" class="ss sis-testimonial_tai"><div class="sc" style="width: 1200px;"><div data-sid="testimonial_tai_0" class="sie-testimonial_tai_0 se" style="transform: scale(1, 1) translate(0px, 0px);"><p class="se-t sie-testimonial_tai_0-text st-m-heading st-d-heading se-rc">- Tal</p></div><div data-sid="testimonial_tai_1" class="sie-testimonial_tai_1 se" style="transform: scale(1, 1) translate(0px, 0px);"><p class="se-t sie-testimonial_tai_1-text st-m-title st-d-title se-rc">You are so amazing! Some of the photos of the kids made me cry! You just capture everything in such a special way! It truly is such a talent. I'm completely obsessed. Cannot thank you enough and can't wait to book my next session in - love them love them love them!</p></div></div></div><div class="ss-s ss-fg"><div class="sc" style="width: 1200px;"><a href="#/" target="_self" class="sie-testimonial_1 se se-stl" data-sid="testimonial_1" data-scrollto="#testimonial" data-state="testimonial|prev|0|0" style="transform: scale(1, 1) translate(0px, 0px) rotate(270deg);"><h3 class="se-t sie-testimonial_1-text st-m-subheading st-d-subheading">— PREV</h3></a><div data-sid="testimonial_2" class="sie-testimonial_2 se" style="width: 1px; transform: scale(1, 1) translate(0px, 0px); top: 334px; left: 905px; height: 1px;"><svg class="se-line" style="width: 26px; height: 2px;"><line data-d-strokelinecap="butt" data-d-linestyle="solid" data-d-thickness="2" data-d-rotatedwidth="26" data-d-rotatedheight="0" data-d-widthoffset="0" data-d-heightoffset="0" data-d-isround="false" data-d-rotation="0" data-d-roundedsolid="false" data-d-dotted="false" data-d-length="26" data-d-mirrorline="false" data-d-dashwidth="21" data-d-spacing="15" data-d-dasharrayvalue="none" data-m-strokelinecap="butt" data-m-linestyle="solid" data-m-thickness="1" data-m-rotatedwidth="26" data-m-rotatedheight="0" data-m-widthoffset="0" 